  "Description": {
    "English": "Specialist <span class=\"name name-stellar\">close combat</span> weapon attachment for the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Multi-Tool</span>. Access fire mode by pressing <span class=\"name name-img\">CYCLEWEAPON</span> and fire weapon with <span class=\"name name-img\">ATTACK</span>.<br><br>The <span class=\"name name-technology\">Scatter Blaster</span> reconfigures the Multi-Tool to heat and shatter <span class=\"name name-earth\">Metallic Elements</span>, firing them in a <span class=\"name name-stellar\">wide cone of destruction</span>. Range is limited, but the shrapnel is highly effective at close range.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "适用于<span class=\"name name-technology\">多用途工具</span>的专业型<span class=\"name name-stellar\">近战</span>武器配件。按下<span class=\"name name-img\">CYCLEWEAPON</span>进入发射模式，使用<span class=\"name name-img\">ATTACK</span>开火。<br><br><span class=\"name name-technology\">散射爆破器</span>重新配置的多用途工具可将加热和捣碎的<span class=\"name name-earth\">金属元素</span>射出，并制造<span class=\"name name-stellar\">锥形的大范围破坏</span>。射程有限，但弹片在近距离范围内非常有效。",
    "TencentChinese": "适用于<span class=\"name name-technology\">多用途工具</span>的专业型<span class=\"name name-stellar\">近战</span>武器配件。按下<span class=\"name name-img\">CYCLEWEAPON</span>进入发射模式，使用<span class=\"name name-img\">ATTACK</span>开火。<br><br><span class=\"name name-technology\">散射迸裂器</span>重新配置的多用途工具可将加热和捣碎的<span class=\"name name-earth\">金属元素</span>射出，并制造<span class=\"name name-stellar\">锥形的大范围破坏</span>。射程有限，但弹片在近距离范围内非常有效。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "<span class=\"name name-technology\">工具組</span>的專家<span class=\"name name-stellar\">近戰</span>武器附加裝置。按 <span class=\"name name-img\">CYCLEWEAPON</span> 進入射擊模式，按 <span class=\"name name-img\">ATTACK</span> 發射武器。<br><br><span class=\"name name-technology\">雙管霰彈槍</span>會重新設定工具組，讓工具組加熱並打碎<span class=\"name name-metal\">金屬元素</span>，再以<span class=\"name name-stellar\">大範圍掃射</span>的方式射出。射程有限，但碎片在短距離之內殺傷力強。"
  },
